title: Conscious. Presents A Night of Giving with Seane Corn
desc: Conscious. Presents: A Night of Giving: Exploring the Power of Women Helping Women Have you ever wondered just what you're putting in your body every month, and how your choices can help women in need? Join Conscious. in an evening raising awareness. Offer your yoga practice, guided by Seane Corn, to empower women and girls at home and around the world. Meet women in our community who are making a difference...and join the cause.  Q&A with Seane, led by Conscious. co-founders Annie Lascoe and Margo Lang, to follow yoga class.  All proceeds will help supply much-needed period products to women in need.
